# Postilize Project Overview

MERN application (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js):
- **Backend**: Node.js 18 with Express, Mongoose, Bull/BullMQ queues, Winston logging
- **Frontend**: React 18, Redux Toolkit + RTK Query, TypeScript, Tailwind + shadcn/ui
- **Database**: MongoDB with Mongoose ODM

## Module Aliases (Backend)
