## API Request/Response Format
```javascript
// Frontend sends data wrapped
body: { data: { field1, field2 } }

// Backend accesses
const { field1, field2 } = req.body.data;

// Response patterns
res.status(200).json({ data });
res.status(400).json({ message: 'Error description' });
```
